{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"cb4aba08f0","title":"对南京军区党委关于是否派军队支持造反派的请示报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7e10fd14d8","index":0,"year":1967,"month":1,"day":21,"articleId":"cb4aba08f0"}],"tags":[{"id":"44b4a39710","name":"林彪","type":"人物"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"abe108b63e","name":"安徽文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/49-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji49":{"comments":[{"id":"9e10ed09e5","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"cb4aba08f0","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"中共中央、国务院、中央军委、中央文革小组1967年1月23日发出了《关于人民解放军坚决支持革命左派群众的决定》"}],"contents":[{"id":"70aa4b08a5","type":"title","text":"对南京军区党委关于是否派军队支持造反派的请示报告\"的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"cb4aba08f0"},{"id":"9e10ed09e5","type":"paragraph","text":"林彪同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"cb4aba08f0"},{"id":"ee6bf9d9a3","type":"paragraph","text":"立派军队支持左派广大群众。请的处","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"cb4aba08f0"},{"id":"4b06cc25f8","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"cb4aba08f0"},{"id":"907f428ed2","type":"paragraph","text":"一月廿一日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"cb4aba08f0"},{"id":"0bf00af831","type":"paragraph","text":"以后凡有真正革命派要求军队支持、援助，都应当这样做。所请不介入，是假的，早已介入了。此事似应重新发出命令回，以前命令作废。请的。又及","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"cb4aba08f0"},{"id":"1f7b41778c","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]中国人民解放军南京军区党委1967年1月21日向中共中央军委副主席林彪并中央军委报告说，“硕接安徽军区报告，首都第三造反司令部驻安徽联络站等单位向安徽军区提出，廿二日到廿三日，在合肥召开15万到20万人大会”，“要安徽军区派出三百到五百名部队警卫会场。他们提出，如派部队就是支持文化大革命，如不派就是不支持文化大革命，并限安徽军区廿一日十四时前答复。是否派部队，请速指示”","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"cb4aba08f0"}],"page":{"id":"1622118390","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"cb4aba08f0","start":276,"end":276}}}},"__N_SSG":true}